item.title: CVE-2018-25019|2024-08-05T12:26:39.672Z -- unknown -- learndash%20lms
item.description: The LearnDash LMS WordPress plugin before 2.5.4 does not have any authorisation and validation of the file to be uploaded in the learndash_assignment_process_init() function, which could allow unauthenticated users to upload arbitrary files to the web server
